ğŸ“¦ Namespaced Resources

These resources exist within a specific namespace, providing a way to partition and organize resources within a single cluster. Each namespaced resource is isolated from those in other namespaces, allowing for multi-tenancy and resource management.â€‹
Percona+2kubecost.com+2Medium+2

Examples include:

    Pods

    Services

    Deployments

    ConfigMaps

    Secrets

    Ingressesâ€‹
