When creating or managing these resources, you specify the namespace they belong to. If no namespace is specified, they default to the default namespace.â€‹

Use Cases:

    Separating environments (e.g., development, staging, production)

    Isolating resources for different teams or projects

    Applying resource quotas and access controls per namespaceâ€‹
